    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, this unit features crisp individual throttle body response and seamless Double VANOS operation. The chassis remains structurally flawless with verified subframe integrity and no stress fractures. Recent preventative maintenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive valve adjustment. It features the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M-differential lock. Zero mechanical defects, no fluid seepage, and a strictly OEM preservation profile make this a turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
