    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, with zero curb rash, wrapped in fresh, period-correct performance tires. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery retains its original matte finish and factory scent, with no softening or bolster wear even on the driver's side. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized specialists, with all fluids recently flushed and filters replaced. The engine bay is meticulously detailed, showing no signs of heat cycling or oxidation. This sale includes the original window sticker, both factory keys, and a complete set of owner's manuals in their original leather portfolio. This is an uncompromising example for the most discerning buyer.",
